{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/nanoporetech/taiyaki/issues/103","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/nanoporetech/taiyaki","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/nanoporetech/taiyaki/issues/103/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/nanoporetech/taiyaki/issues/103/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/nanoporetech/taiyaki/issues/103/events","html_url":"https://github.com/nanoporetech/taiyaki/issues/103","id":742394791,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU3NDIzOTQ3OTE=","number":103,"title":"Bug: naming modified bases with lowercase characters","user":{"login":"marcpaga","id":35224321,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjI0MzIx","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/35224321?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcpaga","html_url":"https://github.com/marcpaga","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcpaga/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcpaga/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcpaga/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcpaga/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcpaga/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcpaga/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcpaga/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcpaga/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcpaga/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","locked":true,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":1,"created_at":"2020-11-13T11:51:59Z","updated_at":"2020-11-13T14:59:07Z","closed_at":"2020-11-13T14:59:07Z","author_association":"NONE","active_lock_reason":null,"body":"If in your references.fasta file you have annotated the modified bases with a lower case character, when reading the fasta file it will be converted to upper case. https://github.com/nanoporetech/taiyaki/blob/589863de71877418a446d083ffe2422d426dcc35/taiyaki/bio.py#L39-L59\r\n\r\nIf you then run something like (notice the lower case m for the 5mC):\r\n`prepare_mapped_reads.py --jobs 32 --mod m C 5mC reads modbase.tsv modbase.hdf5 pretrained/r941_dna_minion.checkpoint modbase_references.fasta`\r\n\r\nThen the alphabet will contain a `m` but the references will contain `M` which leads to a `True` comparison on line 53 (I think) of the linked code. Which then leads to an empty dictionary (if all your references have a an `m`). Thus failing any possible mapping since the reference sequence dictionary is empty.\r\n\r\nEither `.toupper()` should be removed, but might have other consequences downstream; or a simpler and quick fix would be to raise an error if a lower case string is given for  the `--mod` argument.","closed_by":{"login":"marcpaga","id":35224321,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjI0MzIx","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/35224321?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcpaga","html_url":"https://github.com/marcpaga","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcpaga/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcpaga/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcpaga/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcpaga/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcpaga/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcpaga/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcpaga/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcpaga/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/marcpaga/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/nanoporetech/taiyaki/issues/103/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/nanoporetech/taiyaki/issues/103/timeline","per